videos.headline: App State forgets how to snap... and gives up a 90-yard TD in the process
videos.description: Lining up for a field goal, Appalachian State's holder isn't looking for the snap when it hits him, and not only does Georgia Southern pick up the fumble, but Ukeme Eligwe runs it all the back for a 90-yard Eagles touchdown.

videos.headline: Lamb's 30-yard rushing TD breaks game open for App State
videos.description: Nursing a three-point lead, Taylor Lamb keeps the ball on the option and scampers through the defense for 30 yards with a dive to the pylon at the end for the touchdown increasing Appalachian State's lead over Georgia Southern.
